Joanna Riding https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Joanna_Riding 0 Joanna Riding (born Joanne Riding; 9 November 1967) is an English actress. For her work in West End musicals, she has won two Laurence Olivier Awards, and has been nominated for three others. Joanna_Riding ( born Joanne_Riding ; 9_November_1967 ) is an_English_actress .
